The paper deals with facial attribute recognition using deep convolutional neural networks (DCNNs), which is a problem in computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also discusses multi-task optimization and domain adaptation, which are topics in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper involves image and video processing (cs.MM) and optimization algorithms (cs.NE).
